@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get All Routes
GET {{baseUrl}}/routes

### Direct Prediction - Cold weather with snow (requires gritting)
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "route_id": "R001",
    "weather": {
        "temperature_c": -3.5,
        "feels_like_c": -7.2,
        "humidity_pct": 88,
        "wind_speed_kmh": 18,
        "precipitation_type": "snow",
        "precipitation_prob_pct": 85,
        "road_surface_temp_c": -4.2,
        "forecast_min_temp_c": -5.0
    }
}

